title: Screaming Carrot Vegetarian Bakery
description: All vegan bakery and health food shop. Specializes in egg-free and dairy-free baked goods such as savories to take away. A supplier to many local health food shops, and acts as a pick-up point for a local seasonal vegetable box scheme. Directions: from Mansfield Road go along Gregory Boulevard and Foxhall Road is 2nd right.
